S7E1.title: The One with the Jellyfish
S7E1.des:
Ross dates Rachel again after unwittingly
                agreeing to take responsibility for their breakup. Monica is stung by a jellyfish.

S7E2.title: The One with the Cat
S7E2.des:
Phoebe believes that the cat that jumped into
                her guitar case in Central Perk contains the spirit of her adoptive mom.

S7E3.title: The One with the 'Cuffs
S7E3.des:
Monica tries to prove that she can cater a
                gourmet meal for her mother. Chandler gets into an embarrassing situation while dating Rachel's
                boss.

S7E4.title: The One with the Ballroom Dancing
S7E4.des:
Joey teaches the building superintendent
                ballroom dancing to prevent him from evicting Rachel and Monica. Phoebe wants to date a massage
                client.

S7E5.title: The One with Joey's New Girlfriend
S7E5.des:
Joey thinks that Chandler hates Joey's new
                girlfriend -- but the truth is that Chandler avoids her because he is so attracted to her.

S7E6.title: The One with the Dirty Girl
S7E6.des:
Ross's beautiful new girlfriend has a very dirty
                apartment. Chandler becomes more familiar with Joey's girlfriend.

S7E7.title: The One Where Chandler Crosses the Line
S7E7.des:
Chandler is guilt-ridden after kissing Joey's
                girlfriend. Ross's musical talents are not as amazing as he and Phoebe think.

S7E8.title: The One with Chandler in a Box
S7E8.des:
On Thanksgiving, Joey punishes Chandler for
                kissing Kathy. Monica gets a surprise when she visits an eye doctor: He's her former boyfriend's
                son.

S7E9.title: The One Where They're Going to Party
S7E9.des:
The guys try to be spontaneous and wild. Rachel
                is offered a promotion. Monica must decide between a job as a head chef or her catering business.

S7E10.title: The One with the Girl from Poughkeepsie
S7E10.des:
Ross struggles to maintain a long-distance
                relationship. Chandler tries to get a date for Rachel. Monica plots to establish authority at her
                new job.

S7E11.title: The One with Phoebe's Uterus
S7E11.des:
Phoebe's half-brother makes an astounding
                announcement: He has married his older girlfriend and wants Phoebe to be a surrogate mother for
                them.

S7E12.title: The One with the Embryos
S7E12.des:
Phoebe undergoes an embryo transplant and
                becomes pregnant. A simple challenge escalates into a full-blown contest between the guys and the
                women.

S7E13.title: The One with Rachel's Crush
S7E13.des:
Chandler has a hard time with Kathy's new role
                in a play, in which she pretends to have sex with a handsome man. Rachel is attracted to a customer.

S7E14.title: The One with Joey's Dirty Day
S7E14.des:
Joey has no time to shower after he comes home
                from a three-day fishing trip and has to head out to the set of Charlton Heston's new movie.

S7E15.title: The One with All the Rugby
S7E15.des:
Chandler runs into Janice, now divorced, and
                finds her more irritating than ever. Ross plays rugby to impress Emily.

S7E16.title: The One with the Fake Party
S7E16.des:
Rachel throws Emily a phony going-away party so
                she can see Joshua outside of work. Pregnant Phoebe craves meat.

S7E17.title: The One with the Free Porn
S7E17.des:
The guys realize their TV is picking up a porno
                station for free. Phoebe discovers she's carrying triplets.

S7E18.title: The One with Rachel's New Dress
S7E18.des:
Phoebe gets to name one of her babies. Rachel's
                plans to seduce her boyfriend go awry. Ross worries about his relationship with Emily.

S7E19.title: The One with All the Haste
S7E19.des:
Monica and Rachel will do anything to get their
                old apartment back from the guys. Ross asks Emily to marry him.

S7E20.title: The One with the Wedding Dresses
S7E20.des:
Monica wears Emily's wedding dress. Chandler
                forces Joey to get treatment for his snoring at a sleep clinic. Rachel proposes marriage to Joshua.

S7E21.title: The One with the Invitation
S7E21.des:
Rachel and the engaged Ross reminisce separately
                about when they dated each other. The friends get invitations to Ross's wedding.

S7E22.title: The One with the Worst Best Man Ever
S7E22.des:
After Joey almost loses Ross's wedding ring,
                Ross asks both Joey and Chandler to serve as his best man. The girls host a baby shower for Phoebe.

S7E23.title: The One with Ross's Wedding: Part 1
S7E23.des:
In London for Ross's wedding, Chandler and Joey
                argue while sightseeing. After talking with Phoebe, Rachel realizes that she still loves Ross.

S7E24.title: The One with Ross's Wedding: Part 2
S7E24.des:
Phoebe tries to warn the friends that Rachel is
                coming to London. Chandler and Monica develop a connection. Ross's father argues with Emily's
                father.

year:
Chandler makes amends to Joey by spending Thanksgiving
            in a box, Monica finally lands her dream job of head chef, and Phoebe supports her brother.
about:
Chandler makes amends to Joey by spending Thanksgiving
            in a box, Monica finally lands her dream job of head chef, and Phoebe supports her brother.
